function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
--Enable Pit Cannibals
	for i, idCannibal in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup(GRP_FOLLOWERS_PITCANNIBALS)) do
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idCannibal)
			Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idCannibal, false)
	end
--Ealda tethers in Pit
	Hydra.ActorSetAITether(ID_EALDA_01, LOC_PIT)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_EALDA_01, LOC_PIT, "NPC_Run", false)

--Set Barbarians to tether in Pit	
	local tBarbarians = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Step_South_FuryAgainstFate_Barbarians")

	for i, idFollower in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup(GRP_FOLLOWERS_BARBARIANS)) do
		if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower)) then
			Hydra.ActorSetAITether(idFollower, LOC_PIT)
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, LOC_PIT, "NPC_Run", false)
		end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)

--Move Ealda to BannerLoc, place Banner
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(ID_EALDA_01)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_EALDA_01, LOC_BANNER, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(ID_EALDA_01, GIZ_DISPLAY)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_EALDA_01)

--Send Progress Event
	Hydra.EventSend("Move_Ealda_Banner_01", idSelf)

end
